com.wedeploy.android

Class WeDeployEmail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wedeploy.android.BaseWeDeployService<WeDeployEmail>
      • com.wedeploy.android.WeDeployEmail

  • public class WeDeployEmail
extends BaseWeDeployService<WeDeployEmail>
    The WeDeployEmail service enables you to send customized emails to your users and check on their status.

    This class is not thread safe. In order to avoid concurrency issues, you must create a new instance by calling WeDeploy.email(String) for every request you want to do on WeDeployEmail.
